### 1. Costco Anywhere Visa Card by Citi - Best for Gas

**Key specs:**
- Sign-up bonus: $40 Digital Costco Shop Card after first purchase
- Rewards rate: 4% on gas (up to $7K/year), 3% on restaurants and travel, 2% at Costco and Costco.com, 1% on everything else
