## Our Methodology

<div class="methodology">

We evaluate credit cards across 5 criteria:

1. **Rewards value** (40% weight) - Expected return based on typical Gas spending patterns
2. **Sign-up bonus** (25% weight) - Adjusted for minimum spend requirements and timeframe
3. **Fees & APR** (20% weight) - Total cost of ownership including annual fees
4. **Benefits** (10% weight) - Insurance, credits, perks specific to Gas
5. **Ease of approval** (5% weight) - Acceptance rates by credit score tier

Scores are calculated using publicly available data from issuer websites and aggregated user reports. Last updated: 2026-03-13.

